      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"لاَ تُجَالِسُوا شُرَّابَ اَلْخَمْرِ فَإِنَّ اَللَّعْنَةَ إِذَا نَزَلَتْ عَمَّتْ مَنْ فِي اَلْمَجْلِسِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5090 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"Do not sit with those who drink wine, for when the curse descends, it encompasses everyone present in the gathering.\""
        ]
      }
